messages.message: Hey there, do we have a process to add prebuilt apps? (If I want to do some for french market)
That’s great, Leo! @avi @Shubham can help share the details of the process.
I thought I could do french ID card at least and, depending on my frequent French prospect, add more :slightly_smiling_face:

Hi @Léo, that would be great.
You can check the following process and checkpoint (https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/AE/pages/2048655388/Release+Checklist+for+AI+Hub+applications) for releasing an AIHub application. Create a child page under this and you can start tracking each of the item there.
